      "content": "got it. so u mean like a more \"standardized\" look. i had a client ask about hair though—she has natural textured hair/coils and was worried that if she doesn't straighten it or put it in a very tight bun it might look \"unprofessional\" compared to colleagues with straight hair. in your experience, what's the best way to handle natural textures so they don't fall into that \"distracting\" category u mentioned?",
